dataIdInfo.idPurp: TPWD Inland Fisheries Public Waterbodies feature class. This feature class contains statewide geospatial information intended to provide context for mapping purposes.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data is a subset of the National Hydrography Dataset (NHD) generally developed at 1:24,000 scale that has been filtered and modifed for the TPWD Inland Fisheries Division and general agency use. It is projected in the Texas State Mapping System projection.
dataIdInfo.idCredit: The National Hydrography Dataset is a product of the U.S. Gelogical Survey http://www.usgs.gov
